### 6. Chat Widget UI Style Reference

Modern patterns (Intercom/Zendesk/Crisp circa 2025-2026):
- Bot name examples: "Aria", "Max", "Support Bot" — always with avatar (solid circle + letter or icon)
- Status dot: green `#22c55e` for "Online", gray for "Away"
- Escalation flow UX: bot says "I'm connecting you with a human agent. This usually takes 2-3 minutes." Then shows agent card when accepted
- Ticket creation confirmation: inline card, not a new page
- Mobile: full-screen panel below 480px; launcher bottom: 16px, right: 16px
- Accessibility: `role="dialog"` on panel, `aria-live="polite"` on message feed, keyboard-navigable send

