- decisions: Package `@xenova/transformers` is stale/frozen — builder MUST use `@huggingface/transformers@4.2.0`; WASM path is the only path Playwright deploy-test can exercise, so it must be fully functional not a skeleton
- next needs: Builder to wire exact import URLs into demo files; WASM path must produce real answers from the FAQ corpus; WebGPU path is progressive enhancement only
- risks: Qwen2.5-0.5B WASM inference is slow (~3-8s per response in headless) — builder should show a streaming/typing indicator and not let users think the app hung; `@huggingface/transformers` v4 may have minor API differences vs v3 docs online — check pipeline API if anything breaks
